translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 変な趣味に目覚めてしまいそうだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I feel like I'm about to awaken a strange hobby.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これはプレゼントだ、着てほしいな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This is a present; I want you to wear it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 着替えると女エールの姿、おおーびゅりふぉー　男娘ー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After changing clothes, she looks like a female Ale—oh, so beautiful! A trap!
